  description: A Breadcrumb navigation, also known as breadcrumbs, can reduce the number of actions a visitor needs to take in order to navigate to a higher-level page, and improve the discoverability of a websiteâ€™s sections and pages. Like all Shopify based navigations, it uses the [linklist](https://help.shopify.com/en/themes/liquid/objects/linklist) object.
  tags: #linklist
  last_updated: 2018-12-05
  step_1: Place the following code in the `theme.liquid` file, just inside the main content wrapper, or wherever you wish the breadcrumb to appear.
  step_2: To see the breadcrumbs appear, ensure that your site has already been populated with products, collections, blog posts and pages.
